{
  "texts": [
    "A summary of all training hyperparameters can be found in Table 5 in Appendix B.",
    "We compare our approach with previous work and with three strong baselines.",
    "F&G (Fan and Gardent, 2020) is an Encoder-Decoder multilingual model that supports 21 Highand Medium-Resource languages.",
    "The encoder includes structural embeddings and the model was fine-tuned on (silver AMR, human-written text) pairs with data sizes ranging from 400K to 8.2M pairs depending on the target language.",
    "Ribeiro (Ribeiro et al., 2021a) is a mT5 base model that supports 4 HR languages and was fine-tuned on millions of (silver AMR, humanwritten text) and tens of thousands of (human AMR, machine-translated text) pairs for each target language."
  ]
}